Carol Holloway https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carol_Holloway 0 Carol Holloway (April 30, 1892 – January 3, 1979) was an American actress of the silent film era. She appeared in 117 films between 1914 and 1941. She was born in Williamstown, Massachusetts and died in California.
